[{"id":11752,"date":"2023-07-20T15:58:42","modified":"2023-07-20T19:55:26","slug":"aephia-industries-dark-core-roasters-enjoy-a-cup-of-aephian-pulse-drive","link":"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/aephia-industries-dark-core-roasters-enjoy-a-cup-of-aephian-pulse-drive\/","title":{"rendered":"Aephia Industries x Dark Core Roasters &#8211; Enjoy our Aephian Pulse Drive coffee!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video height=\"1080\" style=\"aspect-ratio: 1920 \/ 1080;\" width=\"1920\" controls src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_PULSE_DRIVE_-_ADVERT.mp4\"><\/video><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">To celebrate our 2nd anniversary, we are thrilled to announce a special collaboration with the coffee gurus from Dark Core Roasters!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Today, we unveil <a href=\"https:\/\/darkcoreroasters.com\/products\/aephian-pulse-drive\">Aephian Pulse Drive<\/a>, a limited-edition coffee blend destined to awaken the senses of connoisseurs across the Galia Expanse!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Inspired by the coffee legacy of Aephia&#8217;s employees of old, who relied on this cherished brew to fuel their mining, refining, and ship-crafting endeavors, Aephian Pulse Drive encapsulates the essence of dedication, innovation, and unity, paying homage to the legacy of the past while soaring into the future!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Aephian Pulse Drive is a unique and limited-edition coffee brew that pays tribute to the rich heritage of Aephia Industries. It captures the essence of tradition and craftsmanship, bringing you a delightful blend of ethically sourced, hand-roasted beans from the far reaches of the universe. Carefully curated to tantalize the taste buds with deep natural tones and hints of interstellar spices, this blend emulates the original Atlas Brew but with an extra caffeine infusion.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Embrace this stellar journey and <a href=\"https:\/\/darkcoreroasters.com\/products\/aephian-pulse-drive\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">secure your taste of history today<\/a>! Available for a limited time only.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"11755\" src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-683x1024.png\" alt=\"AEPHIAN PULSE DRIVE 12oz 340g\" class=\"wp-image-11755\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-683x1024.png 683w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-200x300.png 200w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-768x1152.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-1024x1536.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-1365x2048.png 1365w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g-1320x1980.png 1320w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIAN_EXTRACT_-_GROUND_COFFEE_12oz__340g.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"725\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"11754\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER-725x1024.png\" alt=\"AEPHIAN STRONGER TOGETHER\" class=\"wp-image-11754 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER-725x1024.png 725w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER-212x300.png 212w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER-768x1085.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER-1087x1536.png 1087w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER-1449x2048.png 1449w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER-1320x1865.png 1320w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 725px) 100vw, 725px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 725px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 725\/1024;\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stronger Together &#8211; Get Free Coffee!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">To celebrate the launch of this limited-time coffee blend, we have created a giveaway! As today also marks the official launch of our social campaign: <a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/never-alone-stronger-together\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Stronger Together<\/a>, we added a <a href=\"https:\/\/zealy.io\/c\/aephia-stronger-together\/questboard\/6d66771d-2a24-49e1-a556-af4382e87e9e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">quest<\/a> specifically for this collab. Note that<strong> this quest is open to all coffee lovers out there<\/strong> (not only Aephians)! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Completing <a href=\"https:\/\/zealy.io\/c\/aephia-stronger-together\/questboard\/6d66771d-2a24-49e1-a556-af4382e87e9e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">this quest<\/a> requires three steps:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Join the <a href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/8SUGeyEP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Dark Core Roaster Discord<\/a> server.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Say &#8220;Stronger Together&#8221; in the <code><a href=\"https:\/\/discord.com\/channels\/1036746422252486666\/1113345653460959313\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">#english<\/a><\/code> channel<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Participate in the Deadshot game in the <code><a href=\"https:\/\/discord.com\/channels\/1036746422252486666\/1124580919496425622\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">#death-shot<\/a><\/code> channel (by typing <code>\/shot<\/code> at least once!)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Claim the quest on our <a href=\"https:\/\/zealy.io\/c\/aephia-stronger-together\/questboard\/6d66771d-2a24-49e1-a556-af4382e87e9e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">questboard<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This quest will be <strong>open for one week only<\/strong>. The cut-off date is <strong>July 27th, 16:00 UTC<\/strong>. All valid submissions at that time will be added to a raffle. The DCR team will, soon after the end date, draw <strong>8 lucky winners<\/strong>, who each will get a voucher that allows them to order a <strong>free bag of coffee <\/strong>(12oz) in the DCR webshop!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Disclaimer: Though DCR delivers for free in the USA, shipping to other parts of the world is quite costly. You can check shipping on their website to see if it is worth your effort. <em><strong>Shipping is not included in this prize!<\/strong><\/em> Second, if DCR does not ship to your country, we are not able to send you this prize.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"765\" data-src=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER_2-1024x765.png\" alt=\"Aephia x Dark Core Roasters\" class=\"wp-image-11783 lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER_2-1024x765.png 1024w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER_2-300x224.png 300w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER_2-768x574.png 768w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER_2-1536x1148.png 1536w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER_2-2048x1530.png 2048w, https:\/\/aephia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/AEPHIA_-_STRONGER_TOGETHER_POSTER_2-1320x986.png 1320w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1024px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1024\/765;\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Aephia x Dark Core Roasters<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>To celebrate our 2nd anniversary, we are thrilled to announce a special collaboration with the coffee gurus from Dark Core Roasters! Today, we unveil Aephian Pulse Drive, a limited-edition coffee blend destined to awaken the senses of connoisseurs across the Galia Expanse! Inspired by the coffee legacy of Aephia&#8217;s employees of old, who relied on [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1}]